<p>A client is only interested in retrieving notes by class (Note, DocumentReference.class is updated to DocumentReference.category in FHIR R4).  The server responds with the single category of â€˜Clinical Notesâ€™:</p>

<p><strong>Request for DocumentReference note categories</strong></p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>GET [base]/ValueSet/$expand?context=DocumentReference.category&amp;contextDirection=outgoing
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><strong>Response</strong></p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>HTTP/1.1 200 OK
[other headers]
</code></pre></div></div>

